        <p><strong>Salary:</strong> 14 per hour.</p>
        <p><strong>Working Conditions:</strong> Farm hands work outdoors and may handle livestock and equipment. The work environment can vary depending on the type of farm.</p>
        <p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Full-time with varying schedules based on farm needs, including early mornings and weekends.</p>
        <p><strong>Ease of Job:</strong> The job requires physical fitness and a willingness to work in agricultural settings.</p>
