            <a href="#" onclick="showConstructionWorkerProfile()">Household Worker</a>
    
            <div class="jobProfileInfo" style="display: none;">
                <h2>Construction Laborer</h2>
        <p><strong>Job Description:</strong> Construction laborers assist with various tasks on construction sites, including carrying materials, operating machinery, and performing general labor. They work under the supervision of skilled tradespeople.</p>
        <p><strong>Salary:</strong> 16 per hour.</p>
        <p><strong>Working Conditions:</strong> Construction laborers work in diverse environments, including buildings, roads, and bridges. They may need to handle heavy materials and work in different weather conditions.</p>
        <p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Full-time positions with varying shifts based on project requirements, including possible overtime and weekends.</p>
        <p><strong>Ease of Job:</strong> The job involves physical labor and may require lifting and manual tasks.</p>
        <p><strong>Job Location:</strong> Construction sites in the city.</p>
            </div>
            
